{{>layout/header}}
<div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">

    <ol class="carousel-indicators">
        <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
        <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
        <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
    </ol>

    <div class="carousel-inner">
        <div class="carousel-item active">
            <img src="/images/book2.jpg" alt="First Slide">
            <div class="carousel-caption">
                <h3><strong>책 없는 방은 영혼 없는 육체와 같다</strong></h3>
                <p><strong>-키케로-</strong></p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <img src="/images/book3.jpg" alt="Second Slide">
            <div class="carousel-caption">
                <h3><strong>가장 훌륭한 벗은 가장 좋은 책이다</strong></h3>
                <p><strong>-체스터필드-</strong></p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <img src="/images/book4.jpg" alt="Third Slide">
            <div class="carousel-caption">
                <h3><strong>독서에 빠지면 기르던 양이 없어져도 모른다</strong></h3>
                <p><strong>-장자-</strong></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12">
    <div class="col-xs-3">
        <div>회원 수<br><h5>{{allAccountsCount}}</h5></div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-3">
        <div>개설된 스터디<br><h5>{{allStudiesCount}}</h5></div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-3">
        <div>진행중 스터디<br><h5>{{allCloseStudiesCount}}</h5></div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-3">
        <div>종료된 스터디<br><h5>{{allEndStudiesCount}}</h5></div>
    </div>
</div>
